			<description><![CDATA[The surrendered brothers in Madhuban first attend one of the BK centres in India. They study Raja Yoga, adopt a spiritual lifestyle, and do service from their centers. In their centers, they undergo various trainings. To surrender in Madhuban is a decision that would be made by the kumar, his teacher and the main instrument at his center. Surrender is a lifelong commitment and so it takes time and effort to come to that decision. The first step would be to study at your local BK centre.]]></description>
